DATA LICENSE NOTICE:

The datasets included in this replication package are compiled from publicly
available sources and are provided for academic research purposes only.

Data sources include:
- Wind Financial Terminal (proprietary - requires license for commercial use)
- Shanghai Stock Exchange (public data)
- Shenzhen Stock Exchange (public data)
- National Bureau of Statistics of China (public data)
- People's Bank of China (public data)
- Yahoo Finance (public data)
- Robert Shiller's online database (public data)

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with the terms of use and
licensing agreements of the original data providers. Commercial use of
proprietary data sources may require separate licensing.

For questions about data usage rights, please contact the corresponding author.
